a conceptual space;

00:45:28.580 --> 00:45:31.330
it was a physical space, okay.

00:45:31.330 --> 00:45:34.460
And then one more anecdote of
this, and then I'll wrap up.

00:45:34.460 --> 00:45:35.850
At an early convention of Society

00:45:35.850 --> 00:45:40.110
for Ethnomusicology I met a young
African American ethnomusicologist

00:45:40.110 --> 00:45:41.410
named Sylvia Kinney.

00:45:41.410 --> 00:45:43.000
Turned out she was a Detroiter.

00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:46.350
