with or work around.

00:46:59.730 --> 00:47:02.660
Many of these forms are still
around in Greater Detroit,

00:47:02.660 --> 00:47:06.460
at least 20 miles from where
they started, but ethnic --

00:47:06.460 --> 00:47:11.640
