Detroit today, okay.

00:47:31.670 --> 00:47:34.510
Mass transit allowed for
adjacency, and there was less fear.

00:47:34.510 --> 00:47:38.150 position:56%
I'm not saying it was a better
musical model, because one of the --

00:47:38.150 --> 00:47:41.300
I almost didn't start this project
because I'm fighting nostalgia,

00:47:41.300 --> 00:47:42.960
